summary: 9 batch files for ENDGAME classes -----> made for use with Level 1 Main Quest Finished - Abiola the Redguard
descriptionHtml:
Working on a new version for new games with spells items and perks

Note: I will not be adding perks to the current files seeing as how the way i have written it it increases your level and adds perk points. I am currently working on versions with perks though.
Current files do not contain any items future updates will.

9 batch files for ENDGAME classes -----> made for use with Level 1 Main Quest Finished - Abiola the Redguard. All files will level you to about 45
Warning: These do effect your level and you must set perks yourself.

current classes--
Agent
Assassin
Archer
Mage
Paladin
Spellsword
Thief
Warmage
Warrior

If you have any class suggestions just pm me
author: DarthCael
